    {
      "id": "84c331e7_b0ca8710",
      "file_path": "cps-service/src/main/java/org/onap/cps/yang/YangTextSchemaSourceSetBuilder.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 167,
      "message": "I have to comment on the 'keep it short' recommendation. This is very much not the current thinking. I f you read 'clean code' by Robert. C Martin  he states \"Don't be afraid to make a name long. A long descriptive name is better than a short enigmatic name. A long descriptive name is better than a long descriptive comment.\"\n\nfromSourceName does NOT at all imply what this method does createValidIdentifierFromSourceName does make it clearer, so it does add value and is my preferred option between the 2 and I am sure there could be even better names I cant think off right now",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 6639,
        "name": "Toine Siebelink",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "toine.siebelink@est.tech",
        "username": "ToineSiebelink"
      },
      "updated": "2021-02-15 12:10:31.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "bdb4fe1c_57250af5",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "ae9c52f8_954044bc",
      "file_path": "cps-service/src/main/java/org/onap/cps/yang/YangTextSchemaSourceSetBuilder.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 167,
      "message": "You need to read the book and understand it as whole, not as a bunch of independent statements.\nAnd as I mentioned earlier we should follow both good practice not just one.\nThe current thinking is \"the name needs to be as short as reasonable and as expressive as needed it\"\n \nAnd this name \"createValidIdentifierFromSourceName\" is not that. We do not expect to create invalid identifiers or do we?\n\nFrom your response I understand that almost all methods on this class should be renamed then ['forResources', 'toYangTextSchemaSource'].. and I haven't checked other classes. \n\n\nif you have better naming propose it, until now I havent seen a better naming proposal.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 6679,
        "name": "Claudio David Gasparini",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "gasparini24@gmail.com",
        "username": "cdgasparini"
      },
      "updated": "2021-02-15 13:00:23.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "84c331e7_b0ca8710",
      "unresolved": true
    },
